snippet.title: Frisbros Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Launch trailer for Frisbros, my singleplayer/couch coop ultimate frisbee game releasing March 18 2022 to Steam for PC and Mac.
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1481840/Frisbros/
Get the Game for Free: https://thenevel.itch.io/frisbros
